(41, 18, 'Public/Uploads/1538426618.jpg', '婚纱主题类企业官网', '婚纱主题类企业官网', '婚纱主题类企业官网', '1538426618', '&lt;p style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: auto; font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, SimHei, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.hbchryc.com/public/uploads/ueditor/image/20180403/1522748668329494.png&quot; title=&quot;1522748668329494.png&quot; data-bd-imgshare-binded=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; border: none; display: inline-block; max-width: 100%;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: auto; font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, SimHei, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.hbchryc.com/public/uploads/ueditor/image/20180403/1522748668125713.png&quot; title=&quot;1522748668125713.png&quot; data-bd-imgshare-binded=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; border: none; display: inline-block; max-width: 100%;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: auto; font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, SimHei, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.hbchryc.com/public/uploads/ueditor/image/20180403/1522748668258491.png&quot; title=&quot;1522748668258491.png&quot; data-bd-imgshare-binded=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; border: none; display: inline-block; max-width: 100%;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: auto; font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, SimHei, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.hbchryc.com/public/uploads/ueditor/image/20180403/1522748668557261.png&quot; title=&quot;1522748668557261.png&quot; data-bd-imgshare-binded=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; border: none; display: inline-block; max-width: 100%;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 5282, 'Public/Uploads/1538426619.jpeg'),
(42, 25, 'Public/Uploads/1538427004.jpg', '润滑油分销小程序案例（2设计稿）', '润滑油分销小程序案例（2设计稿）', '润滑油分销小程序案例（2设计稿）', '1538427004', '&lt;p style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: auto; font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, SimHei, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;新零售、新营销是近年在大家面前经常出现的关键词，众多实体企业纷纷面临转型的困境，知道出路在哪却不知道该怎么落地，事实上转型移动互联网是一个不错的选择，广西润滑油商城作为一个传统企业，迎接潮流，上线微信小程序商城，结合线下实体店，拓展市场竞争力。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: auto; font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, SimHei, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;润滑油商城小程序作为一款线上电商交易平台，为广大的用户提供了各种润滑油产品讯息，囊括了环保防冻油、低温齿轮油、重负荷齿轮油、抗磨液压油、摩托车机油、通用锂基脂等等。平台集搜索、查询、订阅、交流、下单、购买、评价、反馈、联系等多功能于一体，一站式解决人们的所有需求。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: auto; font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, SimHei, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;对于广大的企业而言，可以通过平台迅速的了解润滑油等行业信息、市场动态、价格走势、消费需求等等，进而迅速的调整经营策略。同时还能够通过平台开启与消费者的直接对话，进而根据消费者的个人需求，提供个性化的定制服务。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: auto; font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, SimHei, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.hbchryc.com/public/uploads/ueditor/image/20180810/1533869674867307.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1533869674867307.jpg&quot; data-bd-imgshare-binded=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; border: none; display: inline-block; max-width: 100%;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: auto; font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, SimHei, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.hbchryc.com/public/uploads/ueditor/image/20180810/1533869674124731.jpg&quot; title=&quot;1533869674124731.jpg&quot; data-bd-imgshare-binded=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; border: none; display: inline-block; max-width: 100%;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 52, 'Public/Uploads/1538427005.jpeg');

